Curves speak louder than words. I can’t back up what my body’s advertisin. 
A segment from spoken word yesterday, this is a clip from a much larger piece
@zainab__k__ thankyouuu yo I was up there for like 15 mins lol I gotta show you the whole thing later
@th_riller yes I want to see the entire thing!
@cynthiasianturi thanks sis!! It’s a segment from a larger piece 😀😀
@th_riller soon!! I’m thinking this summer for sure
@iamdevonwilliams okey lemme know, I’ll take you to a vegan spot 💛
@theutterlyindecent thank youuuu! This was my first time performing this style of poetry 😸
had no idea u were a poet !! Thank u for this- this is soo awesome ✨✨✨
@vr.legacy 😱😱😯 this is true best complement I’ve ever gotten in my life😭😭 thank you 🥰 ❤️❤️❤️

There are those who try HARD to be deep , artistic, and poetic....And then there are those who are living Art themselves🌌A  highly distinct manifestation provided by the universe, one with the universe. You seem to radiate as the description

@raisah.salima thank you❤️❤️❤️😄😄😄 This is a clip, the whole poem is longer. I’ll definitely recite it for you next time or you should come seee meee, I wanna perform it at for a poetry crowd this summa
@th_riller omg yes yessss i would love to come!
Girl YOU KILLED THIS ! Wow. JUST WOW. Completely speechless! I literally had to watch this multiple times to soak it all in!!! Uhhh so much power in this!!!!!!
